  - guid: 1fb45fbd-0041-474f-80d6-726fe2a7c249
    dialogue:
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Katoro
      <Content>k__BackingField: Hello co-worker. Aya seems satisfied. Good for you.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    position: {x: 301, y: 200}
    transitionNode: 0
    entryPoint: 0
    isCheckpoint: 0
    disableAlreadyChosenOptions: 0
  - guid: 4d6c77ef-3a19-470a-b5ac-52d628e6d09c
    dialogue:
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Katoro
      <Content>k__BackingField: There will be some guys on my side on the next round.
        They are smaller than me, so do not worry.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Katoro
      <Content>k__BackingField: While you are beating them up, look at their eye.
        Red eyes mean they can not take much more.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Katoro
      <Content>k__BackingField: Try to take the little guys out before fighting me
        or it could get overwhelming for you.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Katoro
      <Content>k__BackingField: Oh, and when your camera is locked on, you can SWITCH
        TARGETS. Makes it easier to focus.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    position: {x: 905, y: 200}
    transitionNode: 1
    entryPoint: 0
    isCheckpoint: 0
    disableAlreadyChosenOptions: 0
  - guid: 1ec5c792-9681-4fdb-a5df-5c6bf2117da6
    dialogue:
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Katoro
      <Content>k__BackingField: You know how to fight. A bit. That is good. But you
        are a bit helpless.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Katoro
      <Content>k__BackingField: I hope I do not hurt you.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
